<p><a name="Management" id="Management"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bank_for_International_Settlements&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Management">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Management</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>General Manager: <a href="/wiki/Malcolm_Knight" title="Malcolm Knight">Malcolm D. Knight</a> (1 April 2003 -). <a href="/wiki/Andrew_Crockett_(British_banker)" title="Andrew Crockett (British banker)">Andrew Crockett</a> (- 1 April 2003).</li>
