<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFUrofskyPaul_Finkelman2009">Urofsky, Melvin; Paul Finkelman (2002). <i>A March of Liberty: A Constitutional History of the United States Volume II From 1877 to the Present 2nd Edition</i>. Oxford University Press. pp.&#160;674. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0195126378" class="internal">ISBN 0195126378</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+March+of+Liberty%3A++A+Constitutional+History+of+the+United+States+Volume+II+From+1877+to+the+Present+2nd+Edition&amp;rft.aulast=Urofsky&amp;rft.aufirst=Melvin&amp;rft.au=Urofsky%2C+Melvin&amp;rft.au=Paul+Finkelman&amp;rft.date=2002&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B674&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+University+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0195126378&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bank_for_International_Settlements"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
